"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During these eleven days across the country, we have already been able to see some very powerful images, and all the attachment the Greeks have for the flame.\", \"from\": 9932, \"to\": 10090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10064, \"end\": 10070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9969172272071474, \"rank\": 0.0030889906316888503, \"text\": \"Greeks\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now, what a proud and emotional moment it is to officially receive the Olympic flame at the handover ceremony!\", \"from\": 10091, \"to\": 10205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 10206, \"to\": 10221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A big thank you also to our champions Gabriella Papadakis and Beatrice Hess for being at our side to play this powerful and symbolic role as Forerunners of the Paris 2024 Torch Relay,\\\" he added.After crossing the Mediterranean, the Olympic flame will arrive on French soil in Marseille on 8 May.\", \"from\": 10221, \"to\": 10517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10260, \"end\": 10279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriella_Papadakis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriella Papadakis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriella_Papadakis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriella_Papadakis\"}, {\"begin\": 10284, \"end\": 10297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e9atrice_Hess\", \"score\": 0.9999994686535548, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beatrice Hess\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e9atrice_Hess\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e9atrice_Hess\"}, {\"begin\": 10498, \"end