kis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you to the Hellenic Olympic Committee and its President, Spyros Capralos, for this magnificent start to the Olympic Torch Relay in Greece!\", \"from\": 15073, \"to\": 15218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15091, \"end\": 15099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9998374378564399, \"rank\": 9.084585034554237e-05, \"text\": \"Hellenic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 15137, \"end\": 15152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyros_Capralos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spyros Capralos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyros_Capralos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyros_Capralos\"}, {\"begin\": 15188, \"end\": 15207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.521045357810857e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Torch Relay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}, {\"begin\": 15211, \"end\": 15217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999802043933, \"rank\": 1.0611729943837551e-08, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During these eleven days across the country, we have already been able to see some very powerful images, and all the attachment the Greeks have for the flame.\", \"from\": 15219, \"to\": 15377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15351, \"end\": 15357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9969172272071474, \"rank\": 0.0030889906316888503, \"text\": \"Greeks\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now, what a